entry.title: Tahoe Tacks American Gold Star & Silver Concho with Screw Back for Western Tack at Wholesale Price
entry.summary:
Vendor: Derby Originals
Type: Conchos
Price: 1.95

Tahoe Tacks American Gold Star & Silver conchos feature a fancy engraved radial design, with raised 3D gold stars. This concho is perfect for adding a little decorative shine to almost any of your western tack, carry bags, purses, hats, or furniture! Each concho includes a 3/16” chicago screw with a  ⅜” diameter head.

  • DESIGNED TO LAST - these sturdy metal gold star conchos were created to withstand the general daily wear and tear on a variety of items. The elegantly raised 3D design this concho features is meant not only  to look beautiful, but to hold up strong for years to come. These conchos can also be removed and replaced with ease.
    •
  • UNIQUE 3D DESIGN - these stunning conchos by Tahoe Tack feature a beautifully raised star design with unique silver and gold embellishments and are sure to complement your tack set, belt, and more.
    •
  • VERSATILE - With longer screws being sold separately, possibilities are endless. These conchos are designed to compliment a variety of items such as  headstalls, saddles, breast collars, belts, furniture, hats, jackets and much more! 
  • A PLETHORA OF USES - each concho includes a 3/16” Chicago screw, allowing it to be quickly and easily added or removed from almost any item. Compatible with longer or shorter screws, they can be used with western tack such as saddles, headstalls, breast collars, reins, and items such as belts, hats, jackets, furniture, and more!
    •
  • MANY STYLES AND SIZES AVAILABLE - for over 20 years Tahoe Tack has been proud to offer many styles, sizes, and types of conchos to suit your needs. Whether it be attaching a singular concho to a purse or attaching several to a carry bag or saddle, Tahoe Tack has you covered!
    •
